  "specialRules": "Averland lies in the south of the Empire around the Black Fire Pass, a vital and dangerous trade route through the World's Edge and Black Mountains. Averlander mercenary bands are drawn from the Mountainguard that hold the pass, supplemented by expert Marksmen, Bergjaeger trappers/scouts, and the occasional Halfling Scout from the neighbouring Moot. No warband-wide special rule beyond the standard recruitment restrictions (see hero/henchmen entries for unit-specific rules: Bergjaeger Set Traps; Halfling Scout Promotion restriction)."
